<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3949.2.6>
    bibo:endPage "267" ;
    bibo:issue "2" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "239" ;
    bibo:volume "3949" ;
    dc:creator "Bernard, Ernest C.; Soto-Adames, Felipe N.; Wynne, J. Judson" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Collembola of Rapa Nui (Easter Island) with descriptions of five endemic cave-restricted species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231740>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231741>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231742> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231740>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Lateral views of whole specimens. A) Coecobrya kennethi Jordana & Baquero. B) Coecobrya aitorererere n. sp. C) Pseudosinella hahoteana n. sp. D) Seira manukio n. sp. E) Lepidocyrtus olena Christiansen & Bellinger. All scales 200 Μm. Images 7 A, C and D were previously published in BioScience, 64, 711 ‒ 718 (2014)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231740/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231741>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Seira manukio n. sp. A) Dorsal macroseta on dens base. B) Metathoracic claw complex. C) Distal end of dens and mucro. D) Detail of eye patch. E) Dorsal chaetotaxy of head. Open circles represent macrosetae, small filled circles microsetae. F) Chaetotaxy of labium and postlabium. Open circles represent ciliate setae, filled circles are smooth setae, and ‘ V’ represents scales. G) Ventral face of manubrium. H) Mesothorax chaetotaxy. Inset displays alternate arrangement of setae in paratype. I) Metathorax chaetotaxy. J) Chaetotaxy of first abdominal segment." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231741/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.231742>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Seira manukio n. sp., dorsal chaetotaxy. A) Second abdominal segment. B) Third abdominal segment C) Fourth abdominal segment." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/231742/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

